Description: A gokart that the player can ride around wherver they please. [Be wary of monochromatic shells.]
A white horse with a golden horn which leaves a rainbow trail behind as it walks around. [I know it's a horse, but I can only see a cat...]
An ornate carpet players can sit upon to ride. It floats in the air! [This blanket seems to have a will of his own.]
A griaffe. [This isn't what I meant when I said 'golden steed.']
A blue-white amphibious hovercraft with a black bottom. A large fan behind the player provides propulsion.
It's half a bicycle for twice the price. [Squeeky! Squeeky!]
[You better return this to buildmart you vandal!]
[And they said my broken legs were a disadvantage! Hah!]
A stuffed animal head attached at the end of a long wooden stick. [Coconuts not included.]
[Hopefully nobody will notice that your badge is fake.]
A wheelbarrow for you to sit in, with a zombie pushing it. [Like a horse with a carrot, but you're the carrot.]
[Need I say more? Bouncy, Bouncy, Bounce.]
Gives you the swimming on air animation when you are mounted.
